Lord Voldemort is a fictional character from the environment of the books and films about Harry Potter.
His real name is Tom Marvolo Riddle ( in the english original Tom
Marvolo Riddle ) and was born as a son of a Muggle Tom Raddle and Meropa Gaunt.
His mother was the last daughter of the Gaunt family and direct a descendent of Salazar Slytherin.
